      "boundElements": [],
      "updatedAt": 1776582228027,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Each driver = falsifiable thesis:\n  \u2022 name, category, direction\n  \u2022 time_shape: structural|event|cyclical\n  \u2022 thesis + evidence[] (cited)\n  \u2022 target_row, target_subrow (DCF map)\n  \u2022 bull / base / bear + probability\n  \u2022 monitoring_trigger\n\nProducer: Business Understanding",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Each driver = falsifiable thesis:\n  \u2022 name, category, direction\n  \u2022 time_shape: structural|event|cyclical\n  \u2022 thesis + evidence[] (cited)\n  \u2022 target_row, target_subrow (DCF map)\n  \u2022 bull / base / bear + probability\n  \u2022 monitoring_trigger\n\nProducer: Business Understanding",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true
    },
