      "updatedAt": 1776582228027,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Historical facts only (no opinions):\n  \u2022 22 universal rows  (exact list TBD)\n  \u2022 12 common rows  (cogs_ex_da, r&d,\n     capex_total, fcf_traditional, ...)\n  \u2022 derived rows (segment splits)\n\nSame format for ALL companies \u2192\nengine code is reusable.\n\nProducer: Data Extraction",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Historical facts only (no opinions):\n  \u2022 22 universal rows  (exact list TBD)\n  \u2022 12 common rows  (cogs_ex_da, r&d,\n     capex_total, fcf_traditional, ...)\n  \u2022 derived rows (segment splits)\n\nSame format for ALL companies \u2192\nengine code is reusable.\n\nProducer: Data Extraction",
