      "text": "(A)    agent  \u2014 LLM, flexible\n(D)    engine \u2014 code, no shortcuts\n\n\u25a0 green   = drivers / thesis\n\u25a0 blue    = tables / facts\n\u25a0 orange = model / engine\n\u25a0 purple = render output\n\u25a0 red      = gate / blocker\n\n<>   gate (validates, blocks)\n\u2192    data flow\n- ->  dashed = storage / feedback",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "(A)    agent  \u2014 LLM, flexible\n(D)    engine \u2014 code, no shortcuts\n\n\u25a0 green   = drivers / thesis\n\u25a0 blue    = tables / facts\n\u25a0 orange = model / engine\n\u25a0 purple = render output\n\u25a0 red      = gate / blocker\n\n<>   gate (validates, blocks)\n\u2192    data flow\n- ->  dashed = storage / feedback",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
