      "updatedAt": 1776582228027,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Models stored as JSON,\n   not Excel. Excel = render.\n\n2. Modeling is ENGINE (D),\n   not agent. Agent can\n   only supply inputs.\n\n3. Gates between every stage.\n   Shortcut = technically\n   impossible.\n\n4. Memory \u2260 rules.\n   Rules live in hooks.\n   Memory = domain lore only.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Models stored as JSON,\n   not Excel. Excel = render.\n\n2. Modeling is ENGINE (D),\n   not agent. Agent can\n   only supply inputs.\n\n3. Gates between every stage.\n   Shortcut = technically\n   impossible.\n\n4. Memory \u2260 rules.\n   Rules live in hooks.\n   Memory = domain lore only.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 10,
      "autoResize": true
    },
