      "text": "volume \u00d7 price, exit multiple\n\n  \u2022 production_volume  (bbl/day)\n  \u2022 commodity_price\n  \u2022 revenue = volume \u00d7 price\n  \u2022 lifting_cost, opex\n  \u2022 capex (maint + growth)\n  \u2022 FCFF\n  \u2022 terminal: EV/EBITDA exit\n  \u2022 discount: WACC (beta 0.72)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "volume \u00d7 price, exit multiple\n\n  \u2022 production_volume  (bbl/day)\n  \u2022 commodity_price\n  \u2022 revenue = volume \u00d7 price\n  \u2022 lifting_cost, opex\n  \u2022 capex (maint + growth)\n  \u2022 FCFF\n  \u2022 terminal: EV/EBITDA exit\n  \u2022 discount: WACC (beta 0.72)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
