      "updatedAt": 1776582228027,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "standard FCFF (ROIC if capex-heavy)\n\n  \u2022 revenue, cogs, gross_profit\n  \u2022 sga, r&d \u2192 ebit\n  \u2022 tax \u2192 NOPAT\n  \u2022 capex, D&A, \u0394WC\n  \u2022 FCFF = NOPAT + D&A - capex - \u0394WC\n  \u2022 terminal: Gordon perpetuity\n  \u2022 discount: WACC",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "standard FCFF (ROIC if capex-heavy)\n\n  \u2022 revenue, cogs, gross_profit\n  \u2022 sga, r&d \u2192 ebit\n  \u2022 tax \u2192 NOPAT\n  \u2022 capex, D&A, \u0394WC\n  \u2022 FCFF = NOPAT + D&A - capex - \u0394WC\n  \u2022 terminal: Gordon perpetuity\n  \u2022 discount: WACC",
